description: Characterization of secretome of two white rot and two brown rot fungal species grown on aspen. Goal is to utilize temporal sampling to assist in elucidating lignocellulose degradation mechanism

terms.name: Reference
terms.value: Presley GN, Panisko E, Purvine SO, Schilling JS. Comparing the temporal process of wood metabolism among white and brown rot fungi by coupling secretomics with enzyme activities. Appl Environ Microbiol. 2018

title: Spatial connectomics to identify agents relevant to lignocellulose deconstruction in fungi
